# Certchain Verify

## Description
Certchain Verify is a project developed to verify certificates securely using blockchain technology. It helps in ensuring authenticity and preventing fake certificates.

## Features
- Secure certificate verification  
- Prevents data tampering  
- Easy to use system  

## Technologies Used
- Python  
- Machine Learning  

## Project Structure
- main.py – Main execution file  
- model.py – Model logic  
- uv.lock – Dependency file  

## How to Run
1. Install required libraries  
2. Run the following command:
   python main.py  

## Future Scope
- Improve security features  
- Add web interface  
- Enhance performance  

